    "swagger": "2.0",
    "info": {
        "description": "![Smart](/docs/file/logo.png)\r\n\r\n# 概述\r\n\r\n轻量易用的授权基座smart，提供一个非官方RBAC授权模型的基础开箱即用中台管理服务。\r\n\r\n支持响应码自定义国际化、高粒度权限分配、接口路由配置和实时生效，同时支持部门数据权限横向访问限制。\r\n\r\n本系统的全部接口采用【POST】【application/json】方式传输数据。\r\n\r\n除开放接口以外的其他接口均需要通过【ApiKeyAuth:请求头[Token]】完成鉴权。\r\n\r\n系统技术栈：Golang、VueNext、MySQL、Redis、Gin、ArcoDesign\r\n\r\n# 接口文档\r\n\r\n轻度依赖集成，通过静态HTML加载yaml文件进行打开接口文档。\r\n\r\n该接口文档提供Swagger[支持调试]和ReDoc[阅读增强]两个版本。\r\n\r\n[Swagger[支持调试]：/docs/swagger/index.html](http://localhost:8000/docs/swagger/index.html) 丨 [ReDoc[阅读增强]：/docs/redoc/index.html](http://localhost:8000/docs/redoc/index.html)\r\n\r\n## 生成说明\r\n\r\n- 首次集成\r\n\r\ngo install github.com/swaggo/swag/cmd/swag@latest\r\n\r\n- 初始化swagger.yaml文件\r\n\r\nswag init\r\n\r\n- 如果像本工程一样依赖了api.md文件描述项目\r\n\r\nswag init --md .\r\n\r\n- 删除多余的生成\r\n\r\nrm .\\docs\\docs.go\r\n\r\n删除docs.go是因为本项目中并未采用下述依赖来集成。\r\n\r\n而是通过HTML模板+JS+YAML引入集成，移除docs.go用于避免依赖编译报错。\r\n\r\n- github.com/swaggo/swag\r\n- github.com/swaggo/gin-swagger\r\n- github.com/swaggo/files\r\n\r\n源帮助页：[https://github.com/swaggo/swag/blob/master/README_zh-CN.md](https://github.com/swaggo/swag/blob/master/README_zh-CN.md)\r\n",
        "title": "smart",
        "contact": {
            "name": "smart",
            "url": "https://smart.siteol.com",
            "email": "dev@siteol.com"
        },
        "version": "1.0",
        "x-logo": {
            "altText": "smart",
            "url": "/docs/file/logo.png"
        }
    },
    "host": "localhost:8000",
    "basePath": "/",
    "paths": {
        "/docs/sample": {
            "post": {
                "security": [
                    {
                        "Token": []
                    }
                ],
                "description": "系统API基本示例",
                "consumes": [
                    "application/json"
                ],
                "produces": [
                    "application/json"
                ],
                "tags": [
                    "开放接口"
                ],
                "summary": "通用API示例",
                "operationId": "Sample示例",
                "parameters": [
                    {
                        "description": "示例请求",
                        "name": "req",
                        "in": "body",
                        "required": true,
                        "schema": {
                            "$ref": "#/definitions/model.DocsReq"
                        }
                    }
                ],
                "responses": {
                    "200": {
                        "description": "业务受理成功",
                        "schema": {
                            "$ref": "#/definitions/model.DocsOk"
                        }
                    },
                    "400": {
                        "description": "数据校验失败",
                        "schema": {
                            "$ref": "#/definitions/model.DocsVail"
                        }
                    },
                    "401": {
                        "description": "当前尚未登陆",
                        "schema": {
                            "$ref": "#/definitions/model.DocsAuthLg"
                        }
                    },
                    "403": {
                        "description": "权限校验失败",
                        "schema": {
                            "$ref": "#/definitions/model.DocsAuthNg"
                        }
                    },
                    "500": {
                        "description": "服务系统异常",
                        "schema": {
                            "$ref": "#/definitions/model.DocsErr"
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    },
    "definitions": {
